# Quickstart Guide

## Prerequisites

- Python {{ python_version }}+
- [UV](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) package manager
- [go-task](https://taskfile.dev/) task runner
- [pnpm](https://pnpm.io/) for frontend
- {{ container_runtime }} for containers

## Setup

`ash
# Clone and setup
git clone <repository-url>
cd {{ project_slug }}

# Install dependencies
task backend:dev

# Start development server
task backend:serve

# Or use containers
task docker:up
`

## Common Tasks

`ash
# Run tests
task backend:test

# Run linters
task backend:lint

# Format code
task backend:format

# Type check
task backend:typecheck

# Frontend development
task frontend:dev

# Run all containers
task docker:up

# View logs
task docker:logs
`

